- cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper may discuss visualisation techniques for representing flow data. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is another possible category as flow data can be used to study social and information networks. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a potential category as the paper may discuss the societal implications of analysing flow data. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper may discuss data storage and retrieval techniques for flow data.
